      • withTransaction

        <T,E extends Exception> T withTransaction(com.io7m.jfunctional.PartialFunctionType<JFPServerDatabaseTransactionType,T,E> f)
                                   throws E extends Exception
        Evaluate f within a new transaction. The transaction will be committed automatically when f returns, unless f raises an exception.
        Type Parameters:
        E - The type of raised exceptions.
        T - The type of returned values.
        Parameters:
        f - The function to evaluate.
        Returns:
        The value returned by f.
        Throws:
        E - If f raises an exception.
        E extends Exception
